    "tagSetSourceFile": "Named after hailstorms in the ancient Nahuatl language, the Texihuitl is a 170 ton superheavy 'Mech created by RISC as a platform for their Heavy MRM weapons. The 'Mech resembles a longbow, but is built ground up with the single goal of both improving the performance of Heavy MRM launchers and enable the use of the latest experimental RISC technologies."
